De_Station17_underground_beta

This is a beta version of my map so it still has to be tweaked a bit more before the final release.

Background:
Before the combine oppression of City17, all was not well, there was still great stife and civil unrest. One extremist political group had been ignored far too long, in a series of attacks they would bring the city to its knees; the world would hear their demands.
The Terrorists have already begun their attack, derailing a train and blowing a hole in the underground platform giving them direct access to the server room.

Terrorist:
Secure and bomb either the train carrage (A) or the server room (B) to cease all train transport in the city.
You may need to eliminate the CT team so you can later succeed at your objective.

Counter-Terrorists:
Terrorist have stormed the ticket office, killing several civilans, eliminate the threat and stop the bombing at all costs.

Original Half-life 2 station by valve
All additions and modifications are by Ben Andrews.
Any feedback e-mail Benlandrews@aol.com
